                <h1>How to Change Your PS5 Background: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change the background on your PS5, go to Settings, then select "Themes." From there, you can choose "Select Theme" to pick a preset background or "Custom" to upload your own image from a USB drive. Make sure your image is in an appropriate format (JPEG or PNG) and follow the on-screen prompts to apply your new background.</p>
